00:05:53.776 --> 00:05:56.306 A:middle
So what I mean to say is,

00:05:56.306 --> 00:05:59.116 A:middle
you'll end up with
really inaccurate pace,

00:05:59.246 --> 00:06:01.596 A:middle
which is probably much lower
